==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*Ἰδουμαία / Idoumaia / id-oo-mah'-yah

===Etymology===
Of Hebrew origin [[אדום]] /  [[אדם]] {{HH|123}}

===Proper noun===
'''Ἰδουμαία'''

# [[Idumaea]] (that is, [[Edom]]), a region East (and South) of [[Palestine]]: - [[Iduma]].

